<div style="background: #ffffff; font-family: sans-serif; padding: 20px 0px; width:100%; height: 100%">
  <div style="background: #3A4B55; width:300px; padding: 20px;">
    <img src="https://<%= ENV['APPLICATION_HOST'] %>/static/media/vceditor_logo.26b299b6.png" width="100%" />
  </div>
<hr style="border: 1px solid #4ED6CB;" />
<div style="padding-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
  <p>Hi <%= @user.name %>!</p>
  <p>Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

  <p><%= link_to 'Change my password', @reset_password_url.html_safe, {:style => 'color: #4ED6CB'} %></p>

  <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
  <p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>

